tieBreakingRule.text: In the event that two (or more) teams finish with an equal number of points, the following rules break the tie:  1. Head-to-head games between the teams concerned   1a. Points total  1b. Goal difference  1c. Goals scored 2. Goal difference 3. Goals scored
